sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    box rgb(39, 174, 96) Storefront
        participant Customer as Customer
        participant Yves as Yves
    end
    box rgb(41, 128, 185) Spryker Backend
        participant Checkout as Checkout / OMS
        participant OMS as OMS (foreign/ACP SM)
    end
    box rgb(149, 165, 166) External
        participant Melissa as Melissa
        participant Payone as Payone ACP App
        participant Bus as ACP Events Bus
    end

    Customer->>Yves: Submit checkout
    Yves->>Melissa: Verify address [REST]
    Melissa-->>Yves: Address valid
    Yves->>Checkout: Place checkout
    Checkout->>Checkout: Split shipments by warehouse
    Checkout->>Payone: Initialise payment
    Payone-->>Yves: iframe / redirect URL
    Customer->>Payone: Complete payment (iframe/redirect)
    Payone->>Bus: Emit payment event
    Bus-->>OMS: Payment authorised/captured event
    OMS->>OMS: Advance foreign/ACP payment state machine
    OMS->>Checkout: Confirm order
    OMS-->>Customer: Order confirmation email (OMS command)
    Note over OMS: Order queued for export to Plentymarkets
